parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I heard you were looking for me, Commissioner Kimura. Something about a new case?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.So where were you? Your co-worker told me you were out, but he didn’t know why.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Oh, uh, I was out working a case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.I thought Wilkes died of a heart attack.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I think there’s more to it than that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You could say I’m following a hunch.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.A hunch? Do you often follow hunches when working cases?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Sometimes things don’t feel right about a case. I have to figure out if there’s something more to those feelings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Hopefully not wasting department resources, I’m sure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.So what can I do for you, commissioner?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.I guess you could say I’m following a hunch of my own.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.I’m thinking of offering you an opportunity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdSaOp.But it’s getting late in the day now, and we’ll need some time to go over it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.How about we discuss it over dinner? Say, at my place, around 6pm?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.Excellent. Let me give you the address.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Oh, that’s okay, I know where you live.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s just one of the fancier residences in town, and you do have a high profile. People talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.A perfect excuse, but being stalked by a handsome young man might not be such a bad thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx.Oh, and I take it you’ll be wearing something…nicer, for dinner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaAg^.Wow, a dinner meeting with the commissioner! This could be great.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrDe^.I wonder what this opportunity could be.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.When Melissa finds out, she might be upset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.I’ll deal with that when the time comes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp^.First, I’ll need to make a good impression on Andrea. Last time we talked, she caught me snooping around using Melissa’s login.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.I hope I don’t screw things up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe^.I should go prepared. A nice outfit and a bottle of wine is sure to impress.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.I’ve been ordered to escort you out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.At least give me time to collect my stuff.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Where are you going? I don’t recognize you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Where are you going? I don’t recognize you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.The damn security guard took my belt buckle just because it was made of metal.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NPC.Wow! You found my belt buckle! My pants will finally stay up! Take this reward.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This vase is made of metal. I’m not strong enough to break it open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Commissioner Kimura while we’re on the clock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Come with me. We’ll discuss everything in the interrogation room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Sorry, Miss Kimura. I was out of the office this afternoon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.I heard about what happened at the Wilkes’ mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.So... What do we tell the public?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We have to keep this under wraps.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Everyone is convinced that it was a robbery attempt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.This doesn’t have to tie back to the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I know who Nellie is… She was there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.1Hero, you have a specific job. The rest you must trust me with.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Then let me ask you. Should I ignore Nellie or should I arrest her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.If you suspect someone is with the Guild…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Leave them alone and do not interfere.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Okay, Miss Kimura. You can trust me…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.But I will do what I must to keep Lillian safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.She’s safe. The officers will keep guard over her mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I can’t help but feel the need to investigate further. Is there anything I can do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Your focus with the Guild is public relations. If you have the itch to solve crime, then work on your other cases.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.Shit. Why won't she just let me be a part of the undercover team?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoFlEx.I’ve been ordered to escort you out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.At least give me time to collect my stuff.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Did something fall down to the first floor?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnAg.Are you stealing stuff from the office?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Be careful! You can’t let Bobby see you.");
